  - Rapid pre-session intake that fits inside a 60вҖ“80 patient/day clinic workflow, adding zero meaningful time overhead.
  - AI recovery coach pulling data from Whoop, Apple Watch, or other wearables.
  - Protocol recommendation engine: assessment input вҶ’ personalized protocol output. Practitioner interaction must fit inside two minutes.
  - Gamified client recovery app: daily Recovery Score, mobility streaks, XP and levels, visual before/after feedback.
  - Practitioner outcomes dashboard that shows recovery trends across a client base.
