| Google MediaPipe | 33-landmark pose detection, real-time, mobile-ready | `pip install mediapipe` |
| OpenPose (CMU) | 135-keypoint detection (body + face + hands + feet) | GitHub |
| OpenCap | Smartphone video вҶ’ 3D kinematics | `app.opencap.ai` |
| rPPG-Toolbox | Complete HR-from-video pipeline, multiple DL models | GitHub |
| pyVHR | Video-based heart rate estimation | `pip install pyVHR` |
| hrv-analysis | HRV metrics from RR intervals | `pip install hrv-analysis` |
| respmon | Webcam respiratory monitoring | GitHub |
| OpenCV | Video processing, frame extraction, face detection | `pip install opencv-python` |
| SciPy | Signal filtering, frequency analysis | `pip install scipy` |

**Note:** HydraScan uses **QuickPose** (which wraps MediaPipe) rather than raw MediaPipe for the iOS app. The tools above are relevant for backend processing, dataset work, and the rPPG vitals pipeline.


